&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;new new SpringApplication (primarySources).run (args) 我们有一点点的印象&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202309132131719.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20230913213007472&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
